person.bio: Li Jiang 蒋犁 has been a founder, a documentary producer, and an active angel investor and institutional investor in technology at Global Silicon Valley (GSV Capital). He has backed over a dozen tech entrepreneurs working on workforce productivity, resource management, life extension, and blockchain. Li holds an economics degree from Northwestern University and completed coursework at Tsinghua University. He is an adjunct professor at Northwestern’s Farley Center for Entrepreneurship and Innovation.
